## 🚀 Extensibilidade (Como Adicionar Novos Geradores)

### 1. Implementar Interface
```php
class CustomGenerator implements GeneratorInterface
{
    public function generate(GenerationConfig $config): GenerationResult
    {
        // Implementação específica
    }

    public function supports(string $type): bool
    {
        return $type === 'custom_component';
    }
}
```

### 2. Registrar no Service Container
```php
// AppServiceProvider
$this->app->bind(GeneratorInterface::class, CustomGenerator::class);
$this->app->tag([CustomGenerator::class], 'generators');
```

### 3. Criar Template .stub
```php
// app/Domains/Shared/Stubs/Custom/custom.stub
<?php

namespace {{namespace}};

class {{className}}
{
    // Template content with placeholders
}
```

### 4. Implementar Rollback
```php
class CustomGenerator implements GeneratorInterface, RollbackableInterface
{
    public function rollback(RollbackContext $context): RollbackResult
    {
        // Lógica específica de rollback
    }
}
```

